---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 480
  - Title: Maitri Upanishad
    Location: VI 34
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=‘Duo Sunt in Homine’
Format: verse
---
The mind is said to be twofold：
The pure and also the impure;
Impure -- by connection with desire;
Pure -- by separation from desire.
